Five-card infographic: LLM Inference Bottlenecks. 1) VRAM: Model weights + KV-Cache overflow GPU -> Fix: Quantization, Multi-GPU. 2) Memory Bandwidth: Decode is memory-bound -> Fix: PagedAttention, Speculative Decoding. 3) Compute: Prefill needs matmul -> Fix: Tensor Parallelism, Flash Attention. 4) TTFT Latency: First token slow -> Fix: Streaming, small batches. 5) Throughput: Sequential requests -> Fix: Continuous Batching. Icons for each, red problem / green solution.